{"tid":2185053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［重要］本土研：粉嶺哥爾夫球場地契已於8月31日到期 請政府交代是否已獲秘密續約","createTime":"2020-09-02T04:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T07:12:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8817069cdfc8886ad1fc3d03d2264f8c2be41296","tid":2185053,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"【請政府交代粉嶺哥爾夫球場是否已獲秘密續約】<br />\n<br />\n面積達172公頃嘅粉嶺哥爾夫球場，地契已於昨日(2020年8月31日）到期。現時一啲續約嘅消息都無。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BCOLCt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BCOLCt.png&h=17ea133d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本研社今日查冊，都係無發現。公眾對於地價同條款一無所知，甚至連「等待註冊的契約」一欄，都係空嘅，係咪代表政府已經為球場秘密續約？請政府澄清：<br />\n<br />\n【地價】是否已以賤價繼續批出面積達172公頃嘅寶貴土地俾富豪打波？<br />\n<br />\n【年期】新地契簽幾多年？如果同上一份地契年期一樣為21年，2026／27年後，是否不用跟隨「交市值三分一地價」嘅政策？<br />\n<br />\n【房屋發展】當中32公頃作房屋發展嘅土地設三年「過渡期」，詳情是甚麼？會否三年又三年？<br />\n<br />\n【開放政策】有否訂立新條款，要求球場唔好再「扮開放」比市民用？係咪繼續只開放weekdays、日出同日落時間，呢啲唔啱打golf，亦唔會有打工仔得閒嘅時段比公眾？<br />\n<br />\n【開放資料】有否訂立新條款，令政府可以開放球場交俾民政局，交代使用量嘅季度報告(Quarterly Reports)？以往政府借條款之便，利用「第三方資料」理由唔肯公開季度報告，令公眾無法得悉球場點樣使用土地<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為社會焦點轉移，就可以「側側膊，唔多覺」延續土地特權，請公眾一同send email打電話問清楚球場契約嘅最新狀態！<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n【會所場地勁度縮 政府檢討檢碌竹】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bemebG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bemebG&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=fbafe9ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bemebG</a><br />\n<br />\n政府倡私人體育會繳三分一地價　本研社：為何用公帑補貼會所活動？ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/31MotjF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31MotjF&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=681ca81b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31MotjF</a><br />\n<br />\n讓粉嶺高球場再次貢獻香港 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QKKkSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QKKkSc&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=3207cef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QKKkSc</a><br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n支持本土研究社研究工作：<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=595c0960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a><br />\n🖥Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=20572c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/</a><br />\n📸IG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fliberresearch%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=e0d8aac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/liberresearch/</a><br />\n🖨TG: <a href=\"http://t.me/liberinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliberinfo&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=e13c9ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/liberinfo</a><br />\n🐦Twitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LiberResearch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiberResearch&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=a52bccfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LiberResearch</a><br />\n🎥Youtube: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WOIKTk&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=642a2ba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WOIKTk</a><br />\n🧠研究義工報名申請表<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SbbyT3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SbbyT3&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=f6be3670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SbbyT3</a>"},{"pid":"168829